Made to assist you through different shadow working needs, each coffin shaped bath bomb is intentionally created as a healing ritual. Use “Dead to Me” as a cord cutting from a specific person. Try “Bad Blood” for healing childhood wounds and family related trauma. “Monster in the Mirror” deals with self sabotaging behaviors. Or maybe you need “Venom Antidote” to draw out the snakes in your life.
•
Each spell / fragrance is available in a bath bomb or a wax melt if you prefer candle magick. 🕯 now available to US and Canada! Check out @theeleventhhaus website for more magickal self care and supplies.

node.text:
☝︎︎ Carnelian is one of our favorite stones. They are so unique and have such beautiful veining. Come join us tomorrow at our live sale @thecrystalapothecaryco on either FB or IG at 6pm eastern to grab some or you can purchase online at www.TheCrystalApothecaryCo.com. Go enter your email for 10% off coupon when site goes live on 10/1! 
꧁Carnelian stone is said to be a magnet for prosperity and good luck. It's often used by people when they need a healthy dose of good fortune. Because it also functions as a crystal of ambition, determination, and drive, it's believed to protect the wearer from the sluggish energies of incompetent co-workers.
.
.
⭐️ FOLLOW @thecrystalapothecaryco 
.
